OL,3,CJune heatwave cost UK economy more
OL,4,Cthan #1bn, research suggests
OL,6,FLast month's heatwave led to 24
OL,7,Fmillion lost hours of work and cost
OL,8,Fthe UK economy #1.15 billion, research
OL,9,Fsuggests.
OL,11,FWorkers across the country were forced
OL,12,Fto take time off or adjust their hours
OL,13,Fduring the week beginning June 22,
OL,14,Fwhich saw temperatures break the June
OL,15,Frecord.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
