OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784789276
OL,3,CJune heatwave cost UK economy more
OL,4,Cthan #1bn, research suggests
OL,6,FThis suggests there could have been an
OL,7,Fadditional eight million lost hours `
OL,8,Fat an estimated cost to the economy of
OL,9,F#0.38 billion.
OL,11,FThe s87% of the respondents reported
OL,12,Fat least one health-related impact
OL,13,Fduring the week, ranging from
OL,14,Fdisrupted sleep and being more tired
OL,15,Fat work through to a small number of
OL,16,Fworkers reporting more extreme
OL,17,Fsymptoms including dizziness or
OL,18,Ffainting and a faster heartbeat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
