OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784789276
OL,3,CJune heatwave cost UK economy more
OL,4,Cthan #1bn, research suggests
OL,6,FResearchers also found that 5% of
OL,7,Frespondents sought medical attention
OL,8,Fand around 3% reported an accident or
OL,9,Finjury at work during that week, with
OL,10,Faround two-thirds of them feeling it
OL,11,Fwas linked to the weather.
OL,13,FWomen, those aged under 35 and people
OL,14,Fwith existing health conditions were
OL,15,Fthe groups most likely to report that
OL,16,Ftheir health was harmed, the research
OL,17,Ffound.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
