OL,3,CJune heatwave cost UK economy more
OL,4,Cthan #1bn, research suggests
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FElizabeth Robinson, director of the
OL,12,FGrantham Research Institute, said:
OL,13,F"Our findings point to a country that
OL,14,Fremains insufficiently adapted to the
OL,15,Fchanging climate.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
