PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784789276
OL,3,CJune heatwave cost UK economy more
OL,4,Cthan #1bn, research suggests
OL,6,F"The government cannot continue to
OL,7,Fignore extreme heat. Unless it acts
OL,8,Fnow, and makes workplaces safer, we
OL,9,Fare likely to see growing impacts on
OL,10,Fworkers' productivity, health, and the
OL,11,Feconomy."
OL,13,FShouro Dasgupta, environmental
OL,14,Feconomist at the CMCC and visiting
OL,15,Fsenior fellow at the Grantham Research
OL,16,FInstitute, said: "While #1 billion is
OL,17,Flost overall, the greatest effects are
OL,18,Fborne by outdoor workers and those in
OL,19,Fphysically demanding jobs, many of
OL,20,Fwhom are among the lowest paid in the
OL,21,Flabour force.
